WEBVTT

00:13:29.261 --> 00:13:31.955
tada tek počelo suočavati.

00:13:31.955 --> 00:13:34.375
Trebala je proći slijedeća 71 godina

00:13:34.375 --> 00:13:36.229
prije no što je donesen Zakon o ugroženim vrstama,

00:13:36.229 --> 00:13:38.559
no ovo je njegov etos

00:13:38.559 --> 00:13:40.513
sveden na nešto poput scene

00:13:40.513 --> 00:13:42.859
koju biste mogli vidjeti na vitraju.

00:13:42.859 --> 00:13:45.851
Medvjed je bespomoćna žrtva zavezana za drvo,

00:13:45.851 --> 00:13:48.402
a predsjednik SAD-a

00:13:48.402 --> 00:13:50.794
odlučio mu je iskazati milost.

00:13:50.794 --> 00:13:53.440
Hvala.

00:13:53.440 --> 00:13:55.154
(Pljesak)

00:13:55.154 --> 00:13:57.567
[Ilustrirala Wendy MacNaughton]